{"tid":1848304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警同香港人講良心喎","createTime":"2020-01-28T11:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:51:53.000Z","uid":279625,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30d5526b241f87ad26a74228c24268ae48d783e6","tid":1848304,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cXzyb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cXzyb6.png&h=2d5d35ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢叫放炸彈嘅人可唔可以有良心，係呢個咁嚴峻嘅環境裏邊，周圍放炸彈係無良心同不負責任！<br />\n<br />\n我真係成杯飲緊嘅咖啡跌撚咗落地！<br />\n<br />\n周圍放TG無問題，周圍放毒無問題！<br />\n6,7個月咁耐，傷嘅傷，又被跳樓又被跳海，大量被失蹤！<br />\n到底邊個無良心！？<br />\n講你唔聽、唔理，一直迫香港人走投無路！<br />\n政府推出嘅所有政策，都係同香港人玩相反！<br />\n<br />\n出自香港警察口中嘅&ldquo;良心&rdquo;，真係我2020年所聽嘅最難聽嘅説話！！<br />\n回佢一句&ldquo;香港警察，狗屎垃圾！禍港害人，全完自殺！&lsquo;&rsquo;"},{"pid":"dc2e578be66b7a39c4560eecb096811f1bba1fac","tid":1848304,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"3c6cdbe35fb2fc14f72cd6a632a66147e191b669","tid":1848304,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"6d49086a9e5cad1ed4e4ad0c0b43cd7c011b63e7","tid":1848304,"uid":279625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"b959fd2b835d8a80e8eafa2639436b1d67bffd6e","tid":1848304,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTV157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTV157.png&h=a77d0703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝7:00 黎明行動 準時點人數</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as